  "description": "A collection of Specy's instrument themes ported to the Genshin Instruments mod!",
  "body": "<center><img src=https://i.imgur.com/WPMEiK1.png alt=\"Speccy Themes Banner\"></img></center>\n\n---\n\n<center><span><strong>! This resource pack requires <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/genshin-instruments/\">Genshin Instruments</a> v3.3.1 or higher !</strong></span></p></center>\n\n---\n\nThis project provides a collection of resource packs inspired by <a href=\"https://specy.github.io/genshinMusic/\">Specy's Genshin Music App</a>, changing the global look of the instruments in the Genshin Instruments and all its extending mods (i.e <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/evenmoreinstruments/\">Even More Instruments</a>).\n\n\n# Eons of Time\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/specy-themes/version/eons-of-times-1.1\"><img src=https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/iUmXktyN/images/0b363adbe408c7ad281c35d74409c37043605ae7.png></img></a>\n\n# Rainy Lullaby\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/specy-themes/version/sky-music-1.1\"><img src=https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/iUmXktyN/images/f0c9db28c076d5c800dbcf629c0a6bdbbbede44a.png></img></a>\n\n# Snowy Night\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/specy-themes/version/snowy-night-1.1\"><img src=https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/iUmXktyN/images/051f18855521b5e7195361cfd82327fecf94533e.png></img></a>\n\n# Sky Music\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/specy-themes/version/sky-music-1.1\"><img src=https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/iUmXktyN/images/619c465989a5b7f37edda5fb74317695e7f8a960.png></img></a>\n\nFor more, see <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/specy-themes/gallery\">the pack's gallery</a>!\n\n<small>* This project was published under Specy's full permissions</small>",
